	<h2>Windows</h2>
	<p>On Windows 10/8/7/Vista/XP download
	<download prefix="recoil-" suffix="-win64.msi" /> (for 64-bit Windows)
	or <download prefix="recoil-" suffix="-win32.msi" /> (for 32-bit Windows).
	This includes:</p>
	<ul>
		<li>Windows Explorer thumbnails</li>
		<li>plugin for <a href="http://www.xnview.com">XnView [MP]</a></li>
		<li>plugin for <a href="http://www.nyam.pe.kr/dev/imagine/">Imagine</a></li>
		<li>plugin for <a href="http://www.getpaint.net/">Paint.NET</a></li>
		<li>RECOILWin - a standalone viewer</li>
		<li>recoil2png - a command-line converter</li>
	</ul>
